# Accessibility

All auth screens must:

Support screen readers

Provide error announcements

Support large text scaling

Have proper focus order

---

# Testing Requirements

Unit tests:

AuthController

TokenManager

Session logic

Widget tests:

Login screen

Register screen

OTP screen

Integration tests:

Full login flow

Refresh token flow

Logout flow

---

# Performance

Auth state must initialize in <300ms.

Avoid blocking UI on startup.

---

# Cursor Instructions

When generating authentication features:

- Always use AuthController
- Always use Secure Storage for refresh tokens
- Never bypass token lifecycle
- Always implement error states
- Always implement loading states
- Always implement offline behavior